                <h3 class="font-semibold pb-5 underline text-lg">INTRODUCTION</h3>
                <p>In today’s world, every second adds up to innovation or a new wave of technological change. From the first light bulb or telephone to this day, where we have AI assistants, in our phones scheduling our meeting and call logs, we have come a great long way of scientific discovery. Our homes are equipped with smart tools and kits, who know just when to change our room lighting to our increasing dependence on cyberspace. This wave of technological innovation reiterates the importance of the faculty of Emerging Technologies. As a faculty, we aim to create scientific curiosity in the brilliant young minds of this country, who will make use of these emerging technologies to create more unique innovations.

                    Our association with tech-giant like IBM, TCS, and Cyber Dojo is believed to act as leverage of industry collaboration to students, where they can exploit this linkage to get real-life market opportunities from the degree courses.  </p>
